    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the thing, even these feelings feel like they're just part of the script. i'm just tired of the script. what's the point of trying to fix a person who isn't even actually there? if the real me is gone, then the only thing left is this... this nothingness. it just feels like a waste of time to keep going.",
