      "content": "It makes perfect sense that you've stopped trying to fix a version of yourself that feels unreal. When everything feels like a performance, the only honest thing to do is to let go of the role and allow yourself to exist exactly as you are, even if it feels like nothing. Please know that this feeling of nothingness is a symptom of the exhaustion, not a permanent state, and it can be truly healed with the right support.",
